NOTICE FOR THIS REPOSITORY (DERIVED WORK)

This repository contains a derived work: a faithful Python port of the globe
temperature (Tglobe) component of WBGT v1.1. Scope matches the original globe
model.

Modifications and Python translation by Nibir Kanti Roy (Auburn University, 
Auburn, AL, 36849, USA), 2025. All changes are documented in source file 
headers. The original license and acknowledgment above apply to this derived 
work.
